047830023", "uri": "https://scontent.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/39003236_7555878051163356_6726549998324626644_n.png?_nc_cat=108&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=WRF-wN2QkIAQ7kNvgGJt8O_&_nc_ht=scontent.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYAt9HUDq3kJQA69C55dJNrJsPP0VHj-Ouj7_uK1NgPR7w&oe=66E2CF98"}, "display_name": "ChallengeBox Boxing Fitness", "keywords": [], "long_description": "Workout with friends 1vs1.\n\nVariety of workouts to 1vs1:\n1. \ud83e\udd4a Boxing Challenge \n2. \u2692\ufe0f Rock Crusher Challenge\n3. \ud83c\udfb6 Lane Leap Challenge \n\n\ud83e\udd4a Boxing:\nA Full body boxing workout, makes you burn ~200 calories in less than 20 mins. \n\n\u2692\ufe0f Rock Crusher:\nBreak as many as rocks you can in 1 min with hammers in both hands.\nIt's a great STRESS BUSTER \ud83d\udc86\u200d\u2642\ufe0f. \n\n\ud83c\udfb6 Lane Leap:\nDodge the blocks, across lanes. \nGreat for LEGS \ud83e\uddb5 and Core \\\u035d(\u2021)\u035d/\n\nKey Features:\n- Real Time 1vs1 matches\n- Voice chat\n- Weekly Leaderboards\n- Tournaments\n\nJoin our growing community on discord and be part of building new features. \nhttps://discord.gg/NgYUXTtmPH \n\nTry for Free!", "short_description": "Workout with friends 1vs1. \n\nVariety of workouts to 1vs1:\n1. \ud83e\udd4a Boxing Challenge \n2. \u2692\ufe0f Rock Crusher Challenge\n3. \ud83c\udfb6 Lane Leap Challenge "}]}, "developer_name": null, "developer_privacy_policy_url": "https://challengebox.app/privacy", "developer_terms_of_service_url": "https://challengebox.app/toc", "publisher_name": "ChallengeBox LLC", "support_website_url": "https://challengebox.app/", "website_url": "https://challengebox.app/", "category": "APPS", "comfort_rating": null, "comfort_tags": [], "context_category": {"id": "362692211442873", "context_category": "APPS"}, "context_topics": [{"id": "619566195371476"}], "external_subscription_type": "NOT_REQUIRED", "genres": ["SOCIAL", "SPORTS", "FIGHTING"], "has_in_app_ads": false, "internet_connection": "REQUIRED", "play_area": "MOVEME